item.title: tonight / this weekend
item.description: I am having a hell of a time staying on task. I really have NO idea what day it is or where i am. haha. well i know i am on my couch. watching shitty TV and wishing i had an office. But soon it will all change. I have been planning a bit more, attempting to really solidify exactly what i am going to do for the next couple hours.
